A little Java/Processing (http://processing.org) application drawing progressively 
routes as time passes. The routes coordinates, travel times, stay duration and the 
map parameters are read from external files.

See a demo at : http://madewulf.github.com/routedrawer/

To compile, you just need core.jar from the Processing Project. See here for further details on compilation : http://processing.org/learning/eclipse/

